Package asgn2GUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDialog
    Provides base class for dialog boxes used for data entry.
    CargoCanvas
    Creates a JPanel in which graphical components are laid out to represent the cargo manifest.
    CargoFrame
    The main window for the Cargo Manifest graphics application.
    CargoTextArea
    Creates a JTextArea in which textual components are laid out to represent the cargo manifest.
    CargoTextFrame
    The main window for the Cargo Manifest Text application.
    ContainerCodeDialog
    Creates a dialog box allowing the user to enter a ContainerCode.
    LoadContainerDialog
    Creates a dialog box allowing the user to enter information required for loading a container.
    ManifestDialog
    Creates a dialog box allowing the user to enter parameters for a new CargoManifest.
    ManifestManager
    Main programme for the CargoFrame
    ManifestTextManager
    Main programme for the CargoTextFrame
